            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Val</abbr><ex>erio</ex></expan> Saturnino <expan><abbr>vet</abbr><ex>erano</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>ex <expan><abbr>dup</abbr><ex>licario</ex></expan> alae I <expan><abbr>Ulp</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>cont</abbr><ex>ariorum</ex></expan> qui vixit <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>nos</ex></expan> L et <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>Val</abbr><ex>erio</ex></expan> Sabino <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>iti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> I <expan><abbr>ad</abbr><ex>iutricis</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>stip</abbr><ex>endiorum</ex></expan> III vixit <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>nos</ex></expan> XXV filio <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>Caes</abbr><ex>ia</ex></expan> Digna marito et filio <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>aciendum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>uravit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Reicher figürlicher Schmuck; u. a. oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes aedicula mit den Halbkörperbüsten eines jungen Mannes, einer Frau, eines weiteren Mannes und eines Mädchens.</p>
